"Area light ray-traced shadows are described here: :doc:`Raytraced Shadows"
" </render/blender_render/lighting/lamps/area/raytraced_shadows>`."
msgstr ""
"Трассировка теней от ламп-областей описана здесь: :doc:`Трассировка теней"
" </render/blender_render/lighting/lamps/area/raytraced_shadows>`."

